room_title: Escape room "Code Back Slash" by Escape Rooms HQ in Dallas-Fort Worth
room_description:
A response team from Homeland Security has been dispatched to the home of a suspected cyber terrorist. The hacker known as “RedEagle” has been taken into custody. The interrogation revealed he has been compiling a virus to upload into the systems of the New York Stock Exchange.
Your investigation team needs to search the hackers New York apartment and find his server and disable it before the virus makes it to the internet and can’t be stopped. The clock is ticking. Can you crack the code and shut down the virus before it's too late?
